text: Frank Ridge (10 January 1873 - 29 May 1959) was an Australian cricketer. He played four first-class matches for New South Wales in 1895/96. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1873 births Category:1959 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers
